 & \equiv\frac{1}{2}\int d^{3}\mathbf{x}\, dt\left[\dot{\phi}^{2}-(\nabla\phi)^{2}-m^{2}\phi^{2}\right],\label{eq:field rel action}\end{align}

\end_inset 

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\eta^{\mu\nu}=\textrm{diag}(1,-1,-1,-1)$
\end_inset 

 is the Minkowski metric (in this chapter we consider only the flat spacetime)
