The Hilbert space of field states is built in the standard fashion.
 We postulate the existence of the 
\series bold 
vacuum state
\series default 
 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|0\right\rangle $
\end_inset 

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{a}_{\mathbf{k}}^{-}\left|0\right\rangle =0$
\end_inset 

