\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset 

Kruskal
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset 

) and 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|0_{T}\right\rangle $
\end_inset 

 (
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset 

tortoise
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset 

),
\begin_inset Formula \[
\hat{a}_{\pm\omega}^{-}\left|0_{K}\right\rangle =0;\quad\hat{b}_{\pm\Omega}^{-}\left|0_{T}\right\rangle =0.\]

\end_inset 


\layout Standard

Exactly as in the previous chapter, the operators 
