\begin_inset Formula $v_{\mathbf{k}}$
\end_inset 

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{\mathbf{k}}$
\end_inset 

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{\mathbf{k}}$
\end_inset 

